@startuml
title Successful booking, payment and ticket issue

actor Client
participant Booking
participant Users
participant Events
participant Payment
participant Bank
participant Tickets

Client -> Booking: POST /booking/add
Booking -> Users: IsRegistered(clientId)
Users --> Booking: registered
Booking -> Events: TryReserveSeats(eventId, seatIds)
Events --> Booking: reserved
Booking --> Client: booking Reserved

Client -> Booking: POST /booking/pay/{id}
Booking -> Payment: POST /payment/add
Payment -> Bank: TryCharge(clientId, cost)
Bank --> Payment: success
loop for each reserved seat
    Payment -> Tickets: IssueTicket(clientId, eventId, seatId)
    Tickets --> Payment: ticketId
end
Payment --> Booking: payment Succeed
Booking --> Client: booking Paid

@enduml
